VALUES
  ('573ef558-5c05-44fc-a280-d3eeebee4754','ffb5045a-257d-44e3-a88e-fd243c69a15b',100.0,'Owner ~78 (68+ band, peak succession risk)',100.0,'Multi-pharmacist/multi-loc Class A, 57yr tenure (4 loc, 5 pharmacist(s)) | +5 compounding',80.0,'4 coast tell(s): 57yr legacy multi-location group; Three-brother ownership (all 70s+); storefront photos aged / legacy branding; 30+ yr tenure under same owner',65.0,'pharmacy PE consolidation rising; PBM compression = motivated sellers (+5 baseline) | +5 compounding specialty',89.0,'A_acquire_self','A-tier: Carvajal Pharmacy (San Antonio). Owner Raymond, Charles, and Mark Carvajal (3 brothers; Raymond Owner per LinkedIn) ~78, 57yr operation.','Independent retail pharmacy (57yr) in San Antonio, TX. PBM compression + pharmacy PE consolidation = motivated seller pool. Value-add: replace owner-PIC with PharmD operator, deploy modern PIMS / online refill / vaccine clinic, add Med Sync / MTM, monetize compounding or LTC if existing, roll into multi-store platform. Compounding capability = enterprise multiple lift.','high',0.82),
  ('f19d7efa-6c14-441f-adff-08360f67f106','ffb5045a-257d-44e3-a88e-fd243c69a15b',91.0,'Owner ~70 (68+ band, peak succession risk)',93.0,'Multi-pharmacist/multi-loc Class A, 61yr tenure (1 loc, 2 pharmacist(s)) | +5 compounding',80.0,'4 coast tell(s): Legacy 1965 storefront — long-tenured owner; Website domain reflects compounding focus but design appears pre-2015; pre-2015 website or none; storefront photos aged / legacy branding',62.0,'pharmacy PE consolidation rising; PBM compression = motivated sellers (+5 baseline) | -3 inner-city urban (Houston) | +5 compounding specialty',84.0,'B_forward','B-tier: Piney Point Village Pharmacy (Houston). Owner George Tompkins, RPh ~70, 61yr operation.','Independent retail pharmacy (61yr) in Houston, TX. PBM compression + pharmacy PE consolidation = motivated seller pool. Value-add: replace owner-PIC with PharmD operator, deploy modern PIMS / online refill / vaccine clinic, add Med Sync / MTM, monetize compounding or LTC if existing, roll into multi-store platform. Compounding capability = enterprise multiple lift.','medium',0.72),
  ('0f9acad6-04af-402e-be14-abe9ac23eb44','ffb5045a-257d-44e3-a88e-fd243c69a15b',84.0,'Owner ~66 (63-67 band, high succession risk)',85.0,'Solo pharmacist 10+yr Class A (41yr tenure) | +3 banner (GNP/Health Mart)',84.0,'5 coast tell(s): Several staff with 20+ year tenure (loyal but aging staff base); No website; pre-2015 website or none; 30+ yr tenure under same owner; single-store solo PIC operation',60.0,'pharmacy PE consolidation rising; PBM compression = motivated sellers (+5 baseline)',81.0,'B_forward','B-tier: South San Medical Building Pharmacy (San Antonio). Owner Richard Leal, RPh (Owner/Pharmacist) ~66, 41yr operation.','Independent retail pharmacy (41yr) in San Antonio, TX. PBM compression + pharmacy PE consolidation = motivated seller pool. Value-add: replace owner-PIC with PharmD operator, deploy modern PIMS / online refill / vaccine clinic, add Med Sync / MTM, monetize compounding or LTC if existing, roll into multi-store platform. Banner affiliation (GNP/Health Mart) = professional ops; clean PE roll-up integration.','high',0.75),
  ('5f0e2b63-16ba-4aff-b657-c8493978158c','ffb5045a-257d-44e3-a88e-fd243c69a15b',81.0,'Owner ~65 (63-67 band, high succession risk)',85.0,'Solo pharmacist 10+yr Class A (40yr tenure) | +3 specialty (LTC/veterinary)',84.0,'5 coast tell(s): Website appears pre-2015 design (HTTP only); No online refills visible; 40-year-tenured owner; pre-2015 website or none; single-store solo PIC operation',57.0,'pharmacy PE consolidation rising; PBM compression = motivated sellers (+5 baseline) | -3 inner-city urban (Houston)',79.0,'B_forward','B-tier: Citizens Professional Pharmacy (Houston). Owner Nilkanth K Patel (Owner) ~65, 40yr operation.','Independent retail pharmacy (40yr) in Houston, TX. PBM compression + pharmacy PE consolidation = motivated seller pool. Value-add: replace owner-PIC with PharmD operator, deploy modern PIMS / online refill / vaccine clinic, add Med Sync / MTM, monetize compounding or LTC if existing, roll into multi-store platform.','medium',0.68),
  ('6c19120f-8381-43b8-8fe7-eb8b1028ab8e','ffb5045a-257d-44e3-a88e-fd243c69a15b',81.0,'Owner ~65 (63-67 band, high succession risk)',92.0,'Multi-pharmacist/multi-loc Class A, 61yr tenure (1 loc, 8 pharmacist(s))',55.0,'2 coast tell(s): no specialty services; single-store solo PIC operation',60.0,'pharmacy PE consolidation rising; PBM compression = motivated sellers (+5 baseline)',73.0,'B_forward','B-tier: Glenview Professional Pharmacy (Richland Hills). Owner Larry Cowan, RPh; Mita Mehta ~65, 61yr operation.','Independent retail pharmacy (61yr) in Richland Hills, TX. PBM compression + pharmacy PE consolidation = motivated seller pool. Value-add: replace owner-PIC with PharmD operator, deploy modern PIMS / online refill / vaccine clinic, add Med Sync / MTM, monetize compounding or LTC if existing, roll into multi-store platform.','medium',0.7),
  ('9ca58baf-c205-4e3f-a371-4a131a14b43d','ffb5045a-257d-44e3-a88e-fd243c69a15b',87.0,'Owner ~67 (63-67 band, high succession risk)',85.0,'Solo pharmacist 10+yr Class A (60yr tenure) | +3 banner (GNP/Health Mart)',55.0,'2 coast tell(s): no specialty services; single-store solo PIC operation',57.0,'pharmacy PE consolidation rising; PBM compression = motivated sellers (+5 baseline) | -3 inner-city urban (Austin)',72.0,'B_forward','B-tier: Lamar Plaza Drug Store (Austin). Owner Jim and Dorinda Martin (group owners); Lynh Warnken, PharmD (PIC/local owner) ~67, 60yr operation.','Independent retail pharmacy (60yr) in Austin, TX. PBM compression + pharmacy PE consolidation = motivated seller pool. Value-add: replace owner-PIC with PharmD operator, deploy modern PIMS / online refill / vaccine clinic, add Med Sync / MTM, monetize compounding or LTC if existing, roll into multi-store platform. Banner affiliation (GNP/Health Mart) = professional ops; clean PE roll-up integration.','high',0.85),
